#. type: Content of: <sect1><title>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:11
msgid "Rebooting the System"
msgstr "Redémarrer le système"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:13
msgid ""
"Now that all of the software has been installed, it is time to reboot your "
"computer. However, there are still a few things to check.  Here are some "
"suggestions:"
msgstr ""
"Tous les logiciels sont à présent installés. Mais avant de redémarrer votre "
"ordinateur, il y a encore quelques petites choses à vérifier&nbsp;:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:71
msgid ""
"Install any <ulink url='&blfs-book;postlfs/firmware.html'>firmware</ulink> "
"needed if the kernel driver for your hardware requires some firmware files "
"to function properly."
msgstr ""
"Si besoin, installez les <ulink url='&blfs-book;postlfs/firmware."
"html'>micrologiciels</ulink> nécessaires au bon fonctionnement du pilote de "
"noyau de votre équipement."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:80
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Ensure a password is set for the root user."
msgid "Ensure a password is set for the &root; user."
msgstr ""
"Assurez-vous qu'un mot de passe est initialisé pour l'utilisateur root."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:86
msgid ""
"A review of the following configuration files is also appropriate at this "
"point."
msgstr ""
"À ce stade, une relecture des fichiers de configuration suivants s'impose."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:91
msgid "/etc/bashrc"
msgstr "/etc/bashrc"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:92
msgid "/etc/dircolors"
msgstr "/etc/dircolors"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:93
msgid "/etc/fstab"
msgstr "/etc/fstab"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:94
msgid "/etc/hosts"
msgstr "/etc/hosts"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:95
msgid "/etc/inputrc"
msgstr "/etc/inputrc"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:96
msgid "/etc/profile"
msgstr "/etc/profile"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:97
msgid "/etc/resolv.conf"
msgstr "/etc/resolv.conf"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:98
msgid "/etc/vimrc"
msgstr "/etc/vimrc"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:99
msgid "/root/.bash_profile"
msgstr "/root/.bash_profile"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:100
msgid "/root/.bashrc"
msgstr "/root/.bashrc"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:101
msgid "/etc/sysconfig/ifconfig.eth0"
msgstr "/etc/sysconfig/ifconfig.eth0"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:106
msgid ""
"Now that we have said that, let's move on to booting our shiny new LFS "
"installation for the first time! <emphasis>First exit from the chroot "
"environment</emphasis>:"
msgstr ""
"Une fois cela fait, vous pouvez démarrer votre toute nouvelle installation "
"LFS pour la première fois&nbsp;! <emphasis>Tout d'abord, quittez "
"l'environnement chroot</emphasis>&nbsp;:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><screen>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:110
#, no-wrap
msgid "<userinput>logout</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput>logout</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:113
msgid "Then unmount the virtual file systems:"
msgstr "Puis, démontez les systèmes de fichiers virtuels&nbsp;:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><screen>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:115
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<userinput>umount -v $LFS/dev/pts\n"
"mountpoint -q $LFS/dev/shm &amp;&amp; umount $LFS/dev/shm\n"
"umount -v $LFS/dev\n"
"umount -v $LFS/run\n"
"umount -v $LFS/proc\n"
"umount -v $LFS/sys</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>umount -v $LFS/dev/pts\n"
"mountpoint -q $LFS/dev/shm &amp;&amp; umount $LFS/dev/shm\n"
"umount -v $LFS/dev\n"
"umount -v $LFS/run\n"
"umount -v $LFS/proc\n"
"umount -v $LFS/sys</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:122
msgid ""
"If multiple partitions were created, unmount the other partitions before "
"unmounting the main one, like this:"
msgstr ""
"Si plusieurs partitions ont été créées, démontez les autres partitions avant "
"de démonter la principale en exécutant&nbsp;:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><screen>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:125
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<userinput>umount -v $LFS/home\n"
"umount -v $LFS</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>umount -v $LFS/home\n"
"umount -v $LFS</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:128
msgid "Unmount the LFS file system itself:"
msgstr "Démontez le système de fichiers LFS&nbsp;:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><screen>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:130
#, no-wrap
msgid "<userinput>umount -v $LFS</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput>umount -v $LFS</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:132
msgid "Now, reboot the system."
msgstr "Maintenant, redémarrez le système."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:139
msgid ""
"Assuming the GRUB boot loader was set up as outlined earlier, the menu is "
"set to boot <emphasis>LFS &version;</emphasis> automatically."
msgstr ""
"En supposant que le chargeur d'amorçage GRUB a été initialisé comme indiqué "
"plus tôt, le menu est prêt à démarrer automatiquement <emphasis>LFS &version;"
"</emphasis>."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:142
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "When the reboot is complete, the LFS system is ready for use.  What you "
#| "will see is a simple <quote>login: </quote> prompt.  At this point, you "
#| "can proceed to <phrase revision=\"sysv\"> <ulink url=\"https://www."
#| "linuxfromscratch.org/blfs/view/stable/\"> the BLFS Book</ulink></phrase> "
#| "<phrase revision=\"systemd\"> <ulink url=\"https://www.linuxfromscratch."
#| "org/blfs/view/stable-systemd/\"> the BLFS Book</ulink></phrase> where you "
#| "can add more software to suit your needs."
msgid ""
"When the reboot is complete, the LFS system is ready for use.  What you will "
"see is a simple <quote>login: </quote> prompt.  At this point, you can "
"proceed to <ulink url=\"&blfs-book;\">the BLFS Book</ulink> where you can "
"add more software to suit your needs."
msgstr ""
"Une fois le redémarrage terminé, le système LFS est prêt à être utilisé. Ce "
"que vous verrez est une simple invite <quote>login: </quote>. À partir de "
"là, vous pouvez continuer avec <phrase revision=\"sysv\"><ulink "
"url=\"https://www.linuxfromscratch.org/blfs/view/stable/\">le livre BLFS</"
"ulink></phrase><phrase revision=\"systemd\"><ulink url=\"https://www."
"linuxfromscratch.org/blfs/view/stable-systemd/\">le livre BLFS</ulink></"
"phrase> où vous trouverez plus de logiciels pour satisfaire vos besoins."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:148
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "If your reboot is <emphasis role=\"bold\">not</emphasis> successful, it "
#| "is time to troubleshoot.  For hints on solving inital booting problems, "
#| "see <ulink url=\"https://www.linuxfromscratch.org/lfs/troubleshooting."
#| "html\"/>."
msgid ""
"If your reboot is <emphasis role=\"bold\">not</emphasis> successful, it is "
"time to troubleshoot.  For hints on solving initial booting problems, see "
"<ulink url=\"https://www.linuxfromscratch.org/lfs/troubleshooting.html\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Si votre redémarrage ne fonctionne <emphasis role=\"bold\">pas</emphasis>, "
"il est l'heure de dépanner le système. Pour trouver des astuces sur les "
"problèmes du premier démarrage, consultez <ulink url=\"https://www."
"linuxfromscratch.org/lfs/troubleshooting.html\"/>."

